// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1959 — Mass File Rename (blackbasta)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 591a6661-7a33-5945-aaad-56e0aa0019c0

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
